title: Asian Chicken Tray Bake with Broccoli
description: Tonight, fussy eaters, we’re on your side! As a child, chef Lizzie was a very picky eater, but one recipe she couldn't say “no” to was her mum’s one-pan Asian chicken tray bake. Taking a trip down memory lane, Lizzie has recreated her favourite childhood recipe, adding in a couple of twists here and there. Who couldn’t be tempted to the table by sticky chicken!? This dish is about to become your family’s favourite!
